(42, 1, '2014-03-14 17:15:17', '2014-03-14 10:45:17', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDifferent travellers have different idea, way of thinking,finincial status,time limitation and other partinent factors. So we hereby provided some itineraries which are believed to be suit fine with the clients.There are also different characters in driving cars and riding bikes due to their structures and capabilities. We made the itineraries separately for these two types. But, from our experience,motorbikers and SUVs or Camper vans are in a same group because of various matters such as finicial or time limitation so on. At that all participants'' mind sets and attitude should be "in the same boat". This is an important matter what we experienced before. Anyway, 5 days 4 nights /6 days 5 nights and 9 days 8 nights itineraries are mentioned for caravans and motorbikes respectively. The choice is yours (customers ). Our concept "customer is always right ,get his moneys'' worth and we are always at your service." The followings are for the caravans and car rallies-\r\n<h1>5 Days 4 Nights (Thai - Myanmar - India route )</h1>\r\n<h2><strong>Tour code -</strong> <strong>(BVC - 01)</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Day 1 -</strong> incoming from Maesot- Myawaddy- Sein Le Tin Garden Resort (by the road side of Asean highway, 104 mile post ), 7 hrs drive.\r\n<strong>Day 2 - </strong>Sein Le Tin - Naypyitaw, 6 hrs drive.\r\n<strong>Day 3 - </strong>Naypyitaw - Bagan, evening sightseeing.\r\n<strong>Day 4 - </strong>Bagan  morning sightseeing, after lunch proceed to Monywa, 4 hrs drive.\r\n<strong>Day 5 - </strong>Monywa - Kalay - Tamu, 10 hrs drive, after formalities proceed to - India side.\r\n<h2><strong>tOUR cODE - (BVC - 02)</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Day 1 - </strong>Myawwddy - Golden Rock , 8 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 2 - </strong>Golden Rock -Mandalay, 10 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 3 - </strong>Mandalay half day sightseeing - Monywa, 3 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 4 - </strong>Monywa - Kalay, 7 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 5 - </strong>Kalay- Tamu, 3 hrs drive -proceed to India side\r\n<h2><strong>TOUR CODE - (BVC - 03)</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Day 1 - </strong>Myawaddy - Golden Rock\r\n<strong>Day 2 - </strong>Golden Rock - Bagan, 10 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 3 - </strong>Bagan sightseeing - evening 4 hrs drive to Monywa\r\n<strong>Day 4 - </strong>Monywa - Kalay\r\n<strong>Day 5 - </strong>Kalay- Tamu -India side\r\n<h2><strong>TOUR CODE - (BVC - 04)</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Day 1 - </strong>Myawaddy- 115 mile Travellers'' lnn, 12 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 2 - </strong>115 mile - Bagan evening sightseeing, 7 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 3 -</strong> Bagan whole day s /s\r\n<strong>Day 4 -</strong> Bagan -Monywa- Kalay, 11 hrs drive\r\n<strong>Day 5 -</strong> Kalay - Tamu - India side', 'Tour Packages X', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tour-packages1', '', '', '2014-03-24 15:55:59', '2014-03-24 07:55:59', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/?page_id=42', 0, 'page', '', 0),
