(67, 1, '2014-03-15 11:12:10', '2014-03-15 04:42:10', 'Operated Indo- Myanmar Friendship car rally -2012, jointly organized with North East Federation on International Trade (NEFIT)India. It took place 13 to 21 march 2012 covering around 2500 kilometres,19 vehicles and 62 participants were participated. Theme of the rally is '' to promote trade and tourism between India and Myanmar''. It was held in grand scale and higher ranking officials were involved in the flagging - off ceremonies and gala dinners.\r\nOnce again,assigned as a country coordinator by the Ministry of Sports for 2nd time Asean-India car rally ,handled and managed everything successfully the great event from 11 to 15 december 2012. There were 31 suv vehicles (provided by Mahindra)and 112 participants from respective Asean countries and CII and Auto Car personals,incoming from Myawaddy border entry check point,night stopping at Hpa-an, NayPyiTaw,Mandalay, Kalay...covering 1450 kilometres(the whole distance covered was about 8000 kilometres) . In this great event respective Chief Ministers and Union Ministers joined the flagging offs and gala dinners. Also massive local people welcomed and greeted the rally in different towns and villages. Theme of the rally is ''ASEAN-INDIA progress &amp; prosperity.''', 'INDO- MYANMAR FRIENDSHIP CAR RALLY -2012', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bangladesh-china-india-myanmarbcim-tour-2', '', '', '2014-03-15 11:31:06', '2014-03-15 05:01:06', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=67', -1, 'tribe_events', '', 0),
