(170, 2, '2014-03-17 15:39:41', '2014-03-17 09:09:41', 'Different travellers have different idea, way of thinking,finincial status,time limitation and other partinent factors. So we hereby provided some itineraries which are believed to be suit fine with the clients.There are also different characters in driving cars and riding bikes due to their structures and capabilities. We made the itineraries separately for these two types.\r\nBut, from our experience,motorbikers and SUVs or Camper vans are in a same group because of various matters such as finicial or time limitation so on. At that all participants'' mind sets and attitude should be "in the same boat". This is an important matter what we experienced before.\r\nAnyway, 5 days 4 nights /6 days 5 nights and 9 days 8 nights itineraries are mentioned for caravans and motorbikes respectively. The choice is yours (customers ). Our concept "customer is always right ,get his moneys'' worth and we are always at your service."\r\nThe followings are for the caravans and car rallies-', 'Tour Packages', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '42-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-17 15:39:41', '2014-03-17 09:09:41', '', 42, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/42-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
