(173, 1, '2014-03-23 23:00:47', '2014-03-23 15:00:47', '<strong>Date: (13 march to 21 march 2012 )</strong>\r\n\r\nJointly implemented by NorthEast Fedration on International Trade (NEFIT ) based in Guwahati,northeast India and Bright View T&amp; T from Myanmar side. 17 vehicles and 57 India plus 4 Myanmar participants were in this rally. The objectives were to promote friendship and trading among northeast India and Myanmar,especially for Mandalay and Sagaing region. During the trip officials and participants were made courtesy calls with chief ministers of Yangon/Mandalay/Sagaing regions. Also met with higher ranking officials from the ministry of commerce in Nay Pyi Taw and gala dinners were held respectively in Nay Pyi Taw, Yangon,Mandalay and Monywa attended by CMs and their cabinet members. The Embassy of India had also rendered a strong supports to this friendship event. We would say a do worthy and successful trip.\r\n\r\nAs an extended efforts so as to promote friendship &amp; trade among India, Myanmar and Thailand, NEFIT is trying to commence India-Myanmar - Thailand car rally in 2014.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--593" />', 'Indo-Myanmar Friendship Car Rally 2012', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'indo-myanmar-friendship-car-rally-2012', '', '', '2014-03-24 16:52:21', '2014-03-24 08:52:21', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/?p=173', 0, 'post', '', 0),
