(812, 1, '2014-03-26 11:44:25', '2014-03-26 03:44:25', '<p>Date: 25 feburary to 5 march 2014</p>\n<p>3 couples ( Swiss / Spanish / Australian ) came in from Maesot on 3 motorbikes and one landrover and visited along mwd /golden rock /taung gu /mandalay / bagan /monywa / kalay /tamu route and proceeded to India. Among them <strong>Petra &amp; Anders were quite satisfied with our service and they are going to write about us in their website "www.<a href="http://twobikersoneworld.com/" target="_blank">twobikersoneworld.com</a>"  very soon.</strong></p>\n<p><img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--503" /></p>\n', 'Overland driving Myanmar From Thailand To India', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '229-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-26 11:44:25', '2014-03-26 03:44:25', '', 229, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/229-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
