(239, 1, '2014-03-18 02:33:57', '2014-03-17 20:03:57', 'Date: 8 December to 18 December 2013\r\n\r\nA couple of French honeymoon maker &amp;  their friend with 2 motorbikes made 11 days tour along kalay/ monywa /mandalay /bagan / inlay / taung gu / hpa an / myawaddy route. The couple was quite satisfied with our service provided, they wrote about this matter on HUBB and reputation was more and more better in the good books of other new customers.', 'Honeymoon makers and their friend', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '225-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-18 02:33:57', '2014-03-17 20:03:57', '', 225, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/225-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
