(509, 1, '2014-03-22 20:14:54', '2014-03-22 13:44:54', '<strong>A once in a lifetime.</strong>\r\n\r\nIt is great opportunity to have experience riding the steam locomotive in the area of the thousand of the ancient monuments. It is great ancient city Bagan, one of the richest archaeological sites all over the world.\r\n\r\nYou have a great chance riding the antique steam locomotive for forty kilometers among the temples, palm trees, small typical villages and along the small mountain ranges. Unforgettable scenery of the bamboo houses, and very primitive and undespoiled village life of the people.\r\n\r\nAlso the green and very natural beautiful landscape of the extinct volcano Mt.Popa (4981) can be seen and climbed up to the top. The ancient wooden monastery with intricate carvings about the Buddha story can be listed in this wonderful locomotive tour.\r\n\r\n<strong>Not to have regretted, be on locomotive.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are going to inaugurate very soon.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Antique Steam Locomotive', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '155-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-22 20:14:54', '2014-03-22 13:44:54', '', 155, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/155-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(510, 1, '2014-03-22 23:07:49', '2014-03-22 16:37:49', 'Date: 8 December to 18 December 2013\n\nA couple of French honeymoon maker &amp;  their friend with 2 motorbikes made 11 days tour along kalay/ monywa /mandalay /bagan / inlay / taung gu / hpa an / myawaddy route. The couple was quite satisfied with our service provided, they wrote about this matter on HUBB and reputation was more and more better in the good books of other new customers.\n\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--530" />', 'Honeymoon makers and their friend', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '225-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-22 23:07:49', '2014-03-22 16:37:49', '', 225, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/225-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
