(587, 1, '2014-03-22 23:46:17', '2014-03-22 17:16:17', 'Date: 8 July to 13 July 2013\r\n\r\nThere were 4 couples (Austrialian/spanish/chez/Franch ) stuck in Moreh for some days and they were brought to Thailand through Myanmar by us. Spent 6 days 5nights joyously in kalay/monywa/bagan/ yangon &amp; mawlamyaing cities and they amazingly feasted the nature and beauty of Myanmar. Among them S----- couple sent complements to their friends and praise our service rendered to the group. Reputation of us becomes higher and better due to the mouth- to - mouth complements of the customers.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--586" />', 'Overland driving from India to Thailand through Myanmar', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '186-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-22 23:46:17', '2014-03-22 17:16:17', '', 186, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/186-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
