(589, 1, '2014-03-22 23:47:52', '2014-03-22 17:17:52', 'Jointly operated with TransAsiaRoute co.based in Bangkok.27 participants,12 Suvs and 3 motorbikes were participated.Started at 18 june 2013,passed through Myanmar in 4 days 3 nights trip,proceeded to India,then to Bhutan, Nepal and coming back to India. Actully the group was to come back to Myanmar in 8 july 2013,but they were stuck in the Nepal- India border due to some vehicle docuements,they left the vehicles and flew back Thailand. Only in the month of december 2013, they can bring back the vehicles passing through Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--588" />', 'Five countries historical caravan', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '184-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-22 23:47:52', '2014-03-22 17:17:52', '', 184, 'http://192.168.0.123/brightviewtravel/184-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
