(706, 1, '2014-03-23 18:00:48', '2014-03-23 10:00:48', 'Three Indian youngsters/adventurers on one Fortuner Suv had made an overland trip from India, drove 9 days in Myanmar, night stopping at kalay/monywa/bagan/inlay/Yangon/ kyaikhtiyo (golden rock) and proceeded to Thailand for their round trip over the world. Actually we have had no profit at all but we did because their trip meant worldwide. We like to meet their needs as we felt the same way as theirs. So meaningfully rendered our service as much as we could even if our efforts are minute. They were pleased with our service because we arranged a press release with medias, celebrities who had participated in Asean-India &amp; BCIM car rallies and some local Indian people from Indian society in Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--824" alt="" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Great Indian World Trip (27 Sept 13 - 5 Oct 13)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-great-indian-world-trip', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:13:59', '2015-02-14 14:13:59', '', 0, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/?p=706', 0, 'post', '', 0),
