(713, 1, '2014-03-24 17:18:11', '2014-03-24 09:18:11', 'In the month of october a group of Malay Chinese,insisting 58 participants came in on 22 from the entry point of Tamu on 18 Suvs.They drove across Myanmar within 4 days 3 nights trip so intensively. This trip was ( I would say ) a miracle one for both participants and operators. Because the convy stuck on the way kalay to bagan because of heavy rains and they spent nearly 22 hours in a row to reach to bagan. The most memorable character of the participants was that,no one felt bad on a troublesome matter, their optimistic mindset were remarkable. They proceeded according to the tight itinerary and finally we said goodbye eachother at the outgoing border check point.', 'Journey to the west (22 Oct 2013 to 25 Oct 2013)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '710-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:18:11', '2014-03-24 09:18:11', '', 710, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/710-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(714, 1, '2014-03-23 17:00:04', '2014-03-23 09:00:04', 'In the month of november we have operated a Chevrolet brand promotion which took place from 1 to 16 Nov. The brand new 13 no.s of Chevrolet cars came in from Myawaddy, drove to Mandalay, waited for the media group consisting 32 people who were flying from Bangkok. After some activities and visit, proceeded to Bagan, spent a night and televised for another activities, then drove to Yangon. Likewise another 2 media groups ( 48 people ) came flying , visited and televised around the same trip, then flew back Bkk. We made the ground handling service for everything package. Driven distance within 16 days are about 10,000 kms according to the route Myawaddy/Mdy /Bagan/Ygn round trips and after that, proceeded back to Mawlamyaing/ Mwd and Maesot.', 'Chevrolet Show With Media (1 Nov 2013 to 16 Nov 2013)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chevrolet-show-with-media-1-nov-2013-to-16-nov-2013', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:15:44', '2015-02-14 14:15:44', '', 0, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/?p=714', 0, 'post', '', 1),
