(719, 1, '2014-03-24 17:29:33', '2014-03-24 09:29:33', 'Date: 25 feburary to 5 march 2014\r\n\r\n3 couples ( Swiss / Spanish / Australian ) came in from Maesot on 3 motorbikes and one landrover and visited along mwd /golden rock /taung gu /mandalay / bagan /monywa / kalay /tamu route and proceeded to India. Among them petra &amp; Anders were quite satisfied with our service and they are going to write about us in their website "www.<a href="http://twobikersoneworld.com/" target="_blank">twobikersoneworld.com</a>"  very soon.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--503" />', 'Overland driving Myanmar From Thailand To India', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '229-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:29:33', '2014-03-24 09:29:33', '', 229, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/229-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(717, 1, '2014-03-24 17:28:35', '2014-03-24 09:28:35', 'Date: 1 December to 10 December 2013\r\n\r\n7 motorbikes,1 admin logistic car and 10 people rode along Mwd/ golden rock/taunggu /mdy /bgn/ygn/mawlamyaing/Mwd Maesot route.', 'Thai Motorbike Group', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '222-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:28:35', '2014-03-24 09:28:35', '', 222, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/222-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(718, 1, '2014-03-24 17:29:11', '2014-03-24 09:29:11', 'Date: 2 February to 7 February 2013\r\n\r\nA group of 5 people from Netherland came in from Maesot ,rode along mwd/hpa an /ygn/hpn /mwd trip.', 'Norwagians On The Motorbikes Toured In Myanmar', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '228-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:29:11', '2014-03-24 09:29:11', '', 228, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/228-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(722, 1, '2014-03-24 17:36:12', '2014-03-24 09:36:12', 'Date: 8 December to 18 December 2013\r\n\r\nA couple of French honeymoon maker &amp;  their friend with 2 motorbikes made 11 days tour along kalay/ monywa /mandalay /bagan / inlay / taung gu / hpa an / myawaddy route. The couple was quite satisfied with our service provided, they wrote about this matter on HUBB and reputation was more and more better in the good books of other new customers.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--530" />', 'Honeymoon Makers And Their Friend', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '225-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:36:12', '2014-03-24 09:36:12', '', 225, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/225-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
