(735, 1, '2014-03-24 17:59:29', '2014-03-24 09:59:29', 'A big event and friendship activity among Asean countries and India. 31 SUVs and 122 participants from 11 countries. It took nearly one year for preparings. A lot of discussions between relevant organizations were made before the great &amp; remarkable trip took place. Feasibility studies were made by CII and Auto Car experts precisely in advance along the route. These untiring efforts made happened a historical event since all leaders of respective Asean countries and PM India himself cheerfully waved their National flags to welcome the rally participants in New Delhi. This event was held synchronized with Asean-India summit and accomplished more than expected.\r\n\r\nIn this great event "BRIGHT VIEW T&amp;T" was assigned to handle in Myanmar leg and MD was proudly appointed as a country coordinator. Successfully and cheerfully rendered utmost service along 1600 kms, 5 days 4 nights trip.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--563" />', 'ASEAN-India Car Rally 2012', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '180-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 17:59:29', '2014-03-24 09:59:29', '', 180, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/180-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
