(747, 1, '2014-03-24 18:10:15', '2014-03-24 10:10:15', 'In the month of October 2013, a group of Malay Chinese, consisting 58 participants came in on 22 from the entry point of Tamu on 18 Suvs. They drove across Myanmar within 4 days 3 nights trip so intensively. This trip was ( I would say ) a miracle one for both participants and operators. Because the convoy stuck on the way kalay to bagan because of heavy rains and they spent nearly 22 hours in a row to reach to bagan. <strong>The most memorable character of the participants was that, no one felt bad on a troublesome matter, their optimistic mindset were remarkable.</strong> They proceeded according to the tight itinerary and finally we said goodbye each other at the outgoing border check point.', 'Journey to the west (22 Oct 2013 to 25 Oct 2013)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '710-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 18:10:15', '2014-03-24 10:10:15', '', 710, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/710-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
