(850, 1, '2014-04-03 02:30:23', '2014-04-02 18:30:23', 'In the month of October 2013, a group of Malay Chinese, consisting 58 participants came in on 22 from the entry point of Tamu on 18 Suvs. They drove across Myanmar within 4 days 3 nights trip so intensively. This trip was ( I would say ) a miracle one for both participants and operators. Because the convoy stuck on the way kalay to bagan because of heavy rains and they spent nearly 22 hours in a row to reach to bagan. <strong>The most memorable character of the participants was that, no one felt bad on a troublesome matter, their optimistic mindset were remarkable.</strong> They proceeded according to the tight itinerary and finally we said goodbye each other at the outgoing border check point.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" alt="" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--849" />', 'Journey to the west (22 Oct 2013 to 25 Oct 2013)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '710-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-03 02:30:23', '2014-04-02 18:30:23', '', 710, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/710-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
