(869, 3, '2015-02-14 22:13:50', '2015-02-14 14:13:50', 'Date: 8 July to 13 July 2013\r\n\r\nThere were 4 couples (Austrialian/Spanish/Chez/French ) stuck in Moreh for some days and they were brought to Thailand through Myanmar by us. Spent 6 days 5 nights joyously in Kalay/Monywa/Bagan/ Yangon &amp; Mawlamyaing cities and they amazingly feasted the nature and beauty of Myanmar. Among them Spanish couple sent complements to their friends and praise our service rendered to the group. Reputation of us becomes higher and better due to the mouth-to-mouth complements of the customers.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--586" alt="" />', 'Overland driving from India to Thailand through Myanmar', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '186-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:13:50', '2015-02-14 14:13:50', '', 186, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/186-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(870, 3, '2015-02-14 22:13:59', '2015-02-14 14:13:59', 'Three Indian youngsters/adventurers on one Fortuner Suv had made an overland trip from India, drove 9 days in Myanmar, night stopping at kalay/monywa/bagan/inlay/Yangon/ kyaikhtiyo (golden rock) and proceeded to Thailand for their round trip over the world. Actually we have had no profit at all but we did because their trip meant worldwide. We like to meet their needs as we felt the same way as theirs. So meaningfully rendered our service as much as we could even if our efforts are minute. They were pleased with our service because we arranged a press release with medias, celebrities who had participated in Asean-India &amp; BCIM car rallies and some local Indian people from Indian society in Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--824" alt="" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Great Indian World Trip (27 Sept 13 - 5 Oct 13)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '706-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:13:59', '2015-02-14 14:13:59', '', 706, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/706-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(873, 3, '2015-02-14 22:14:27', '2015-02-14 14:14:27', 'In the month of October 2013, a group of Malay Chinese, consisting 58 participants came in on 22 from the entry point of Tamu on 18 Suvs. They drove across Myanmar within 4 days 3 nights trip so intensively. This trip was ( I would say ) a miracle one for both participants and operators. Because the convoy stuck on the way kalay to bagan because of heavy rains and they spent nearly 22 hours in a row to reach to bagan. <strong>The most memorable character of the participants was that, no one felt bad on a troublesome matter, their optimistic mindset were remarkable.</strong> They proceeded according to the tight itinerary and finally we said goodbye each other at the outgoing border check point.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--849" alt="" />', 'Journey to the west (22 Oct 2013 to 25 Oct 2013)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '710-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:14:27', '2015-02-14 14:14:27', '', 710, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/710-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(874, 3, '2015-02-14 22:14:37', '2015-02-14 14:14:37', 'Jointly operated with TransAsiaRoute co.based in Bangkok.27 participants,12 Suvs and 3 motorbikes were participated.Started at 18 june 2013,passed through Myanmar in 4 days 3 nights trip,proceeded to India,then to Bhutan, Nepal and coming back to India. Actully the group was to come back to Myanmar in 8 july 2013,but they were stuck in the Nepal- India border due to some vehicle docuements,they left the vehicles and flew back Thailand. Only in the month of december 2013, they can bring back the vehicles passing through Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--588" alt="" />', 'Five countries historical caravan', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '184-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:14:37', '2015-02-14 14:14:37', '', 184, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/184-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(876, 3, '2015-02-14 22:14:54', '2015-02-14 14:14:54', '<p style="text-align: justify;">An ancient city of 11 AD situated by the Ayarwaddy river. Numerous artifacts of old pagodas to be seen at least 2 days for a rush traveler and at least 6 months for a researcher. Including 4/5 stars ratings and other classes accommodation facilities cum sorts of European /Chinese / Myanmar traditional foods available. Really a must for tourists.</p>\r\n<img class="alignnone" style="border: 7px solid #ddddff;" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/baganmy1-300x206.jpg" alt="bagan" />', 'Bagan', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '448-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:14:54', '2015-02-14 14:14:54', '', 448, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/448-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(881, 3, '2015-02-14 22:15:53', '2015-02-14 14:15:53', 'Date: 25 feburary to 5 march 2014\r\n\r\n3 couples (Swedish/ Belgium/ Italian  ) came in from Maesot on 3 motorbikes and one landrover and visited along mwd /golden rock /taung gu /mandalay / bagan /monywa / kalay /tamu route and proceeded to India. Among them <strong>Petra &amp; Anders were quite satisfied with our service and they are going to write about us in their website "www.<a href="http://twobikersoneworld.com/" target="_blank">twobikersoneworld.com</a>"  very soon.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--503" alt="" />', 'Overland driving Myanmar From Thailand To India', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '229-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:15:53', '2015-02-14 14:15:53', '', 229, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/229-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(882, 3, '2015-02-14 22:16:07', '2015-02-14 14:16:07', 'Date: 8 December to 18 December 2013\r\n\r\nA couple of French honeymoon maker &amp;  their friends with 2 motorbikes made 11 days tour along kalay/ monywa /mandalay /bagan / inlay / taung gu / hpa an / myawaddy route. <strong>The couple was quite satisfied with our service provided, they wrote about this matter on HUBB and reputation was more and more better in the good books of other new customers.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://locahost/brightviewtravel/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--530" alt="" />', 'Honeymoon Makers And Their Friend', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '225-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-14 22:16:07', '2015-02-14 14:16:07', '', 225, 'http://locahost/brightviewtravel/225-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
